Established procedures, documented in Refinery Instruction RI-362 "Process Safety Information", guide employees on how to keep PSI up to date, accurate, and readily available to employees. PSI is kept current by following established management of change (MOC) process. Electronic files of most PSI are maintained on the Refinery Information Server. Locations of electronic and hard copies of all PSI are specified in RI-362. Personnel have access to either the hard copies or electronic copies on a 24-hour basis.  PSI includes:



