- California Permissible Exposure Limits;

- ACGIH Emergency Response Planning Guidelines (ERPGs), U.S. EPA Acute Exposure Guideline Levels (AEGLs), and California Office of Environmental Health Hazard Assessment acute and eight-hour Reference Exposure Levels (RELs); and

- Corrosion data (Fixed Equipment Reliability Corrosion Monitoring Location thickness values).



